sdp/verification/t-016@20260502t001347zb-verify.md:13:The script now exercises six endpoints: `GET /health`, `POST /memory/search`, `POST /beats/next`, `GET /world/entities?limit=1`, `GET /world/entities/{entity_id}` (conditional), and `GET /events?limit=1`. Every call prints `METHOD PATH -> STATUS` on one line, matching the spec exactly. The `--verbose` flag appends `body=<first-200-chars>` to each line, newlines escaped to keep output single-line. `--entity-id` flag and `NARRATIVE_ENTITY_ID` env var are honoured; when absent, the entity ID is auto-extracted from the list response. URL-encoding of the entity ID via `urllib.parse.quote` is correct. Exit code 0 iff all calls return 2xx.
